    <item>
      <title>沙特选择提高亚洲油价后油价小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯出人意料地向亚洲买家提高了主要级别的价格，投资者等待美联储有关美国货币政策的线索，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:24:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔作证前股市小幅波动：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，股市和国债小幅波动，因为交易员在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发表证词之前采取谨慎立场，预计他将重申降息缺乏紧迫性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
